{"type": "article", "id": 18031, "title": "亚麻产品包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-25T06:50:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143355ovHGaN4tYUdCO5PE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tKLÄSSBOLS 是瑞典一家传统做亚麻的品牌，目前已传至第四代了。新的包装设计来自瑞典设计师 Tobias Möller 和 Rasmus Erixon，采用不完全封口的牛皮纸盒，上面的缺口露出亚麻布的花纹，与纯色的牛皮纸构成软和硬、复杂和简单的对比。盒子上的缺口其实是用两片牛皮纸重叠，加上牛皮纸本身的一种复古感，令人觉得舒服。大大小小的产品排在一起有温和居家的气质。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143353ifUN2GYvDJTOMC3t.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143353toBLeU86gNWqOujD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061433549OS7DcAZC6PdoLtY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143354YiHJItd3xv95rPka.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}